~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
version 0.8.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* added a better init.d script for startup, now supports stop/start. Will need to run setup.py in order to get the new file, or copy src/startup_artillery to /etc/init.d/artillery

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
